prompts.frontCover:
Minimalist greeting card front, flat 2D vector art, clean illustration style with simple elegant shapes. On a plain, off-white background, a humorous scene unfolds. A cartoon illustration of Lao Lao from the photo, wearing her blue sweatshirt and black pants, is playfully perched atop Jordan's shoulders. Jordan, illustrated from the photo in his tan hoodie and dark pants, is comically wobbling and trying to balance, his knees slightly bent, with a funny, strained but happy expression. Lao Lao has a wide, triumphant grin and is holding a single, lit birthday candle like a victory torch. Simple, whimsical confetti shapes in pastel colors float gently around them.

Centered below the illustration, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! Thanks for always lifting me up."
